{
  "stem": "4078.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We decorated it, and it was nice, it was comfortable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However, when we first moved to this flat, we had to share this Anderson Shelter, which-- they had different sizes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But apparently when they built it in this particular house, they built it just for this family, who were a mother, father, and two children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had an old mother living there who refused absolutely to go into the shelter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She wanted to stay into the-- in the-- in the flat, her flat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she wouldn't go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we came, and things got so bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course bombs were flying, and the-- you could hear the planes overhead and just hope that they would go over and they wouldn't drop bombs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then you'd hear the guns trying to shoot them out, and you'd see the-- the lights.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was, it was pretty scary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I really wasn't-- I wasn't petrified, I really wasn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was just a little nervous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we went to the shelter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then I felt safe there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "However, it was very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because there were the other-- other family, and then we were there, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So it was very, very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Until this family decided they weren't going to stay in London anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they moved out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they moved away, so then we had the shelter to ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then we made it very comfortable, put a sort of a-- a bed, a mattress there and-- and a-- a little bed for me and shelves.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They told you not to put shelves up because the vibration from bombing made everything fall down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we put shelves, because you had to you know, put your stuff away somewhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
